OL,5, It was, perhaps, the most expensive    
OL,6, fast-food item ever consumed in        
OL,7, Ljubljana.                             
OL,9,FThis particular burek - a Balkan cross 
OL,10,Fbetween a pie and pasty - cost a       
OL,11,Ffamished delivery rider 400 euros      
OL,12,F(#350). All because he sat down on the 
OL,13,Fsteps of a church to tuck into his     
OL,14,Fsnack during the Slovenian capital's   
OL,15,Ffirst Covid lockdown.                  
OL,17,FThe scene was caught on camera. And the
OL,18,Fphoto of police surrounding a worker   
OL,19,Fwho was taking food to others - for the
OL,20,Fcrime of having a quick bite of his own
OL,21,F- quickly became a cause celebre.      
